data.description: Established Dearborn neighborhood offers this 3 bedroom bungalow that awaits its new owners. Hardwood floors throughout the lower level. Large bay window allows plenty of light.  Updated Kitchen with dining nook... All appliances stay, built in oven and cooktop, Also includes the washer and dryer.  Large 2nd floor master. Furnace and HWH 2018. Roof replaced in 2017.  Plenty of extra room in the partially finished basement that also features a 2nd Kitchen area. Fenced yard and paver patio.  Some light cosmetic work needed. Sale is contingent on the Sellers getting a new home under contract. City inspection has been scheduled. Pre-Approved Buyers Only!
